bilingual.source: They held each other by the tail.
The tail and fin help steer it.
bilingual.target: 尾巴和鳍帮助控制方向。

bilingual.source: I have a bushy tail, he said.

bilingual.target: 扎克站起来看了看他的尾巴。

list.abstract: head 与 tail 就像它的名字一样的浅显易懂，它是用来显示开头或结尾某个数量的文字区块，head 用来显示档案的开头至标准输出中，而 tail 想当然就是看档案的结尾

yingyinNormal.en: Look, the tail points at twelve.
yingyinNormal.zh: 尾巴指向12点方向。

yingyinNormal.en: Let's play pin the tail on the mammoth.
yingyinNormal.zh: 嘿!我们来玩帮长毛象钉尾巴!

yingyinNormal.en: The snake that eats its own tail, forever and ever.
yingyinNormal.zh: 蛇吞吃自己的尾巴，无休无止。

yingyinNormal.en: You are standing on my tail, though. Off, off! I'm sorry.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你踩到我尾巴了，快挪开！对不起。

yingyinNormal.en: It's got a tail. Oh, tables don't have tails. There's a handle as well. What can it be?
yingyinNormal.zh: 它有一条尾巴。噢，桌子可不会有尾巴。还有一个把手呢。这到底是什么东西？

yingyinNormal.en: The cat? What cat, honey? That Siamese with blue eyes and a broken tail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 那只猫咪？什么猫咪，宝贝？蓝色眼睛，尾巴断掉的暹罗猫。

yingyinNormal.en: Anyway, I don't wanna do it in front of someone with a tail. Hey, you swore you would nerve tell.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不想在有尾巴的人面前打。你发誓不说的。

yingyinNormal.en: Nine, ten. Ready or not, here we come. George, I can see your wiggly tail.
yingyinNormal.zh: 九十，躲好了吗，我们来找你了。乔治，我看见你左摇右摆的尾巴了。

yingyinNormal.en: What, my watch stopped. My watch. Okay, see, the, the dinosaur tail isn't going around any more.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？我的表停了，我的表，好，你看，这个恐龙指针的尾巴不动了。

yingyinNormal.en: And this bit is the tail of the crab, so we just snap that bit off, because it's not very tasty, there's no meat there.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这部分是螃蟹的尾巴，扯下来就好，因为它不太好吃，没有肉。

yingyinNormal.en: Mr. Dinosaur does not have a tail anymore. Poor George. You have had Mr. Dinosaur a long time.
yingyinNormal.zh: 现在恐龙先生的尾巴好像没有了。可怜的乔治。你的恐龙已经陪伴你很长时间了。

yingyinNormal.en: That's not a trumpet, Peppa. You found Mr. Dinosaur's tail. Oh. Now, Daddy Pig can mend him.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这个可不是号角佩奇气，你找到了恐龙先生的尾巴。哦。现在，猪爸爸能修好它了。

yingyinNormal.en: Till finally she has no choice but to go back home with that cute fuzzy wuzzy little tail between her legs to become...
yingyinNormal.zh: 终于发现自己只能选择回家，夹着自己那条毛茸茸的小尾巴，变成了…

yingyinNormal.en: When I heard that Joffrey's dog had tucked tail and run from the Battle of the Blackwater, I didn't believe it. But here you are.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我听说黑水河之战时乔佛里的狗儿夹着尾巴跑了，我还不相信，可你跑到这儿了。

yingyinNormal.en: When I turned tail and ran, this dumb shank stayed behind to help Alby.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我四处逃命的时候，这个笨蛋留在那儿救埃尔比。

yingyinNormal.en: We have a tail. Who is he? We're after the same thing, and I can help you.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们被人追踪了。他是谁？我们都在追查同一个目标，而我能帮你。

yingyinNormal.en: One of the tail-end Nexus 8s. He looks like he could take your head off. He tried.
yingyinNormal.zh: 新发现的旧型号复制人吗? 看他这么壮似乎都能把你的头给砍下来了。他刚才正想那么干呢。

yingyinNormal.en: And City Hall is right up my tail to find them. This is priority number one. Assignments.
yingyinNormal.zh: 市政厅天天追在我屁股后面，这是头等大事，任务分配。

yingyinNormal.en: So, what, you find yourself some local tail and you just completely forget what team you're playing for?
yingyinNormal.zh: 怎么你找了一个当地的马子，就忘了自己的身份了吗？

yingyinNormal.en: Now, the tail should come off quiet easily, so you just pull that off. The claws, they just come off as well, so just pull that off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 虾尾很好剥，拔下来就行了。爪子也会脱落，拔下来就行了。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: We'd give it a moving head and <highlight>tail</highlight> and put a scent on it to make it smell like a real rat.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我们会给它安装一个活动的头和尾巴，并在它身上放一种气味，让它闻起来像一只真正的老鼠。
